ano?

474
00:32:16,090 --> 00:32:17,260
Ano ang tinitingnan mo?

475
00:32:18,078 --> 00:32:20,251
Hindi kami nandito para abalahin ka ng husto.

476
00:32:20,782 --> 00:32:23,259
Nandito lang kami for a little getaway.

477
00:32:23,390 --> 00:32:26,896
Oh, at sige lang at maging kalmado.

478
00:32:28,682 --> 00:32:30,000
Kung handa na kayong lahat,

479
00:32:30,205 --> 00:32:31,533
mangyaring sundin ako sa ganitong paraan.

480
00:32:32,970 --> 00:32:33,696
Tama.

481
00:32:36,213 --> 00:32:38,142
Magiging komportable na tayo rito, Auntie.

482
00:32:41,380 --> 00:32:42,097
dalisay.

483
00:32:42,659 --> 00:32:43,577
puro!

484
00:32:44,103 --> 00:32:44,891
Halika na!

485
00:32:44,930 --> 00:32:47,579
Paumanhin tungkol doon, Da Zhan.
Ang aking kaibigan ay medyo…

486
00:32:50,539 --> 00:32:51,647
Ang gwapo mo, U.

487
00:32:52,013 --> 00:32:53,100
Mukhang thug.

488
00:32:53,848 --> 00:32:55,100
Katulad mo, kuya.

489
00:32:56,607 --> 00:32:58,995
Mangyaring lumiko sa kabilang panig.

490
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:01,960
Chin up, please.

491
00:33:02,325 --> 00:33:03,462
Maglagay ng malaking ngiti.

492
00:33:03,493 --> 00:33:04,254
U.

493
00:33:21,533 --> 00:33:22,302
Hilaga.

494
00:33:34,160 --> 00:33:35,678
Magsisimula na ba tayo?

495
00:33:37,232 --> 00:33:38,198
ganito?

496
00:33:39,340 --> 00:33:40,600
yun lang.

497
00:33:45,590 --> 00:33:48,385
-Iyan ay perpekto.
- Napakasaya ko para sa kanya.

498
00:33:48,550 --> 00:33:50,103
Hindi ko maiwasang maging proud sa kanya.

499
00:33:59,800 --> 00:34:01,699
Napakaromantiko ng lugar na ito,
hindi mo ba iniisip?

500
00:34:03,580 --> 00:34:04,598
Ito ay napakarilag.

501
00:34:04,780 --> 00:34:06,099
Ito ay lubos na romantiko.

502
00:34:12,488 --> 00:34:13,202
U.

503
00:34:13,940 --> 00:34:15,397
Gusto kong magpakasal dito,

504
00:34:15,961 --> 00:34:16,822
at ngayon.

505
00:34:17,299 --> 00:34:17,976
Hmm?

506
00:34:18,327 --> 00:34:18,899
Hmm.

507
00:34:30,180 --> 00:34:30,951
Lolo.

508
00:34:34,789 --> 00:34:35,930
May itatanong ako sayo.

509
00:34:38,180 --> 00:34:40,096
Pwede ba akong magpakasal dito ngayon?

510
00:34:40,914 --> 00:34:41,395
ano?

511
00:34:41,431 --> 00:34:42,502
Pakiusap, Lolo?

512
00:34:43,580 --> 00:34:46,542
Gusto kong maging puno ang kasal ko
sa lahat ng taong mahal ko.

513
00:34:47,900 --> 00:34:49,902
Ayokong magpakasal
sa harap ng mga estranghero.

514
00:34:50,656 --> 00:34:52,699
Ayokong mag-peke ng isa pang ngiti.

515
00:34:53,528 --> 00:34:54,278
Pero sa tingin ko—

516
00:34:54,297 --> 00:34:56,395
Ang tanong ko lang ay iyon
Ikakasal ako dito ngayon.

517
00:34:56,988 --> 00:34:58,601
Tungkol naman sa kasal sa Bangkok…

518
00:35:01,350 --> 00:35:03,697
Papayag akong 'isagawa' ito.

519
00:35:04,750 --> 00:35:07,402
Gusto kong maging maganda ang kasal ko.

520
00:35:10,170 --> 00:35:11,400
Tinatanong mo ako niyan?

521
00:35:11,857 --> 00:35:12,500
Oo!

522
00:35:13,220 --> 00:35:14,017
ayos lang.

523
00:35:14,788 --> 00:35:17,397
papayag ako.

524
00:35:17,980 --> 00:35:19,094
Salamat, Lolo!

525
00:35:19,149 --> 00:35:19,899
U!

526
00:35:20,826 --> 00:35:22,720
Pupuntahan ko ito, ginoo.

527
00:35:22,838 --> 00:35:24,299
Pakiusap. salamat po.

528
00:35:28,022 --> 00:35:29,106
At ikaw, Pai?

529
00:35:30,108 --> 00:35:32,600
Ayaw mo bang magpakasal
nandito din ngayon?

530
00:35:38,370 --> 00:35:39,102
ginagawa ko.

531
00:35:39,590 --> 00:35:41,002
Gusto kong magpakasal ngayon, Lolo.

532
00:35:45,622 --> 00:35:46,345
Ay, Pai.

533
00:35:48,120 --> 00:35:49,401
Hayaan mong yakapin ko rin siya.

534
00:35:49,431 --> 00:35:50,431
Sige. Halika na.

535
00:35:50,456 --> 00:35:51,696
Tim, yakapin ko si Pai.

536
00:35:56,130 --> 00:35:57,945
sobrang saya ko.

537
00:35:58,850 --> 00:36:01,262
Maaari ka bang magdagdag ng higit pang mga upuan?

538
00:36:01,280 --> 00:36:03,198
Ang uri ng frame ay mukhang walang laman ngayon.

539
00:36:03,240 --> 00:36:04,400
Syempre naman ma'am.

540
00:36:07,561 --> 00:36:08,997
Ito ba ang lahat ng upuan?

541
00:36:10,070 --> 00:36:11,746
Siguro maaari mong subukang ilagay ang mga ito muna.

542
00:36:16,222 --> 00:36:16,980
Mr. Pai.

543
00:36:17,392 --> 00:36:21,798
Nagpadala ako ng tsuper para sunduin si Mr. Prem,
G. Kuea, Ms. Oom, at ang iyong mga magulang.

544
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:23,210
Dapat nandito na sila agad.

545
00:36:24,035 --> 00:36:24,982
Salamat, Nana.

546
00:36:25,350 --> 00:36:26,096
Syempre.

547
00:36:30,269 --> 00:36:30,980
Nana.

548
00:36:31,853 --> 00:36:32,600
Oo?

549
00:36:33,696 --> 00:36:36,397
Salamat sa lahat.

550
00:36:43,250 --> 00:36:44,202
Oo, sir.

551
00:36:44,955 --> 00:36:47,395
pasensya na po.

552
00:36:58,340 --> 00:36:59,054
Tim.

553
00:37:01,910 --> 00:37:03,657
Gawin natin ito
ang huling kasal namin.

554
00:37:06,804 --> 00:37:07,659
pangako ko.

555
00:37:11,980 --> 00:37:14,801
Kailangan ko ring magpasalamat sa inyong lahat.

556
00:37:16,136 --> 00:37:20,220
Kahit kailan sa buhay ko hindi ko naisip
Magkakaroon ako ng ganoon kasaya na pamilya.

557
00:37:21,811 --> 00:37:24,604
Lahat kayo ay nagpaparamdam sa akin na ako ay nararapat.

558
00:37:26,410 --> 00:37:29,100
Mangyaring hayaan mo akong manatili sa iyo
sa buong buhay mo,

559
00:37:29,290 --> 00:37:33,022
Hilaga, Tim, Pai.

560
00:37:40,250 --> 00:37:41,398
Nakaka-touch yun.

561
00:37:42,822 --> 00:37:43,502
Ngunit…

562
00:37:44,287 --> 00:37:48,497
Hindi ko naisip
darating din ang araw na ito.

563
00:37:50,160 --> 00:37:52,202
Halos hindi kami nakarating
napakaraming beses kanina.

564
00:37:53,610 --> 00:37:55,546
Salamat sa inyong dalawa.

565
00:37:56,231 --> 00:37:57,202
At ikaw din, U.

566
00:37:58,310 --> 00:38:00,662
Masaya ako na nandito kami ngayon.

567
00:38:02,940 --> 00:38:03,997
Masaya rin ako,

568
00:38:04,900 --> 00:38:07,401
na nalampasan namin ang lahat.

569
00:38:08,540 --> 00:38:09,740
mahal ko kayong lahat.

570
00:38:17,117 --> 00:38:17,871
Aking turn?

571
00:38:20,100 --> 00:38:22,200
Wala akong gustong sabihin.

572
00:38:22,862 --> 00:38:23,757
Baka umiyak na ako.

573
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:25,702
Halika, Tim.

574
00:38:27,554 --> 00:38:28,499
mahal ko kayong lahat.

575
00:38:31,767 --> 00:38:32,456
Guys.

576
00:38:33,180 --> 00:38:35,450
Gusto kong gumawa ng time capsule.

577
00:38:35,980 --> 00:38:38,700
Ngunit hindi ko iniisip na ibaon ito dito
ay isang magandang ideya.

578
00:38:38,808 --> 00:38:41,702
Hindi namin ito mahuhukay
kung sakaling kailanganin nilang i-renovate ang lugar.

579
00:38:42,310 --> 00:38:46,059
Gagawa na lang ba tayo ng video
na maaari nating tingnan sa loob ng limang taon?

580
00:38:48,121 --> 00:38:48,702
Oo naman.

581
00:38:48,757 --> 00:38:52,072
Okay. Magsisimula na ako ngayon.

582
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,060
Hilaga,

583
00:38:58,070 --> 00:38:59,497
ngayon ang araw ng iyong kasal.

584
00:38:59,854 --> 00:39:00,857
Nagawa mo.

585
00:39:01,825 --> 00:39:03,499
I wish you happiness.

586
00:39:03,659 --> 00:39:04,894
Mahalin mo silang lahat.

587
00:39:05,616 --> 00:39:07,604
Mahal na mahal kita.

588
00:39:08,188 --> 00:39:10,200
At mahalin mo rin ang iyong mga kuya.

589
00:39:11,410 --> 00:39:12,402
Kahanga-hanga ka.

590
00:39:12,531 --> 00:39:13,401
Nagawa mo!

591
00:39:14,540 --> 00:39:15,798
U, turn mo naman.

592
00:39:16,002 --> 00:39:16,602
Tama.

593
00:39:17,557 --> 00:39:20,200
U, hindi ka na nag-iisa.

594
00:39:20,630 --> 00:39:23,102
Mayroon kang North, at isang mapagmahal na pamilya.

595
00:39:23,228 --> 00:39:24,798
Mayroon kang Tim at Pai.

596
00:39:25,131 --> 00:39:26,397
Siguraduhing mahal mo si North.

597
00:39:27,240 --> 00:39:28,002
mahal kita.

598
00:39:32,714 --> 00:39:34,200
Susunod...

599
00:39:35,161 --> 00:39:36,200
Gawin natin ito, Pai.

600
00:39:38,579 --> 00:39:39,800
Ano ang dapat kong sabihin?

601
00:39:41,770 --> 00:39:43,600
Kahit anong gusto mo
upang sabihin sa iyong sarili sa hinaharap.

602
00:40:41,210 --> 00:40:43,902
Ako, Thanin Chaiyanuwat,

603
00:40:44,930 --> 00:40:50,706
kunin ang Jirachote Jeeramongkolthanun
para maging legal na kasal kong asawa.

604
00:40:57,857 --> 00:41:01,100
Ako, si Jirachote Jeeramongkolthanun,

605
00:41:02,470 --> 00:41:07,260
kunin si Thanin Chaiyanuwat
para maging legal na kasal kong asawa.

606
00:41:09,340 --> 00:41:11,800
Ako, si Issara Preechajit,

607
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:17,801
kumuha ng Nipitphon Jeeramongkolthanun
para maging legal na kasal kong asawa.

608
00:41:19,210 --> 00:41:22,801
Ako, Nipitphon Jeeramongkolthanun,

609
00:41:23,460 --> 00:41:28,460
kunin si Issara Preechajit
para maging legal na kasal kong asawa.

610
00:42:05,510 --> 00:42:10,302
Isinusumpa kong mamahalin at mananatiling tapat sa iyo

611
00:42:14,072 --> 00:42:15,200
para sa mas mahusay

612
00:42:18,915 --> 00:42:19,739
o para sa mas masahol pa.

613
00:42:19,830 --> 00:42:22,094
…At pagkatapos ay pinalawak namin ito.

614
00:42:22,520 --> 00:42:23,718
PRASIT PONGSANG
ISANG DAAN AT DALAWAMPUNG MILYON

615
00:42:23,754 --> 00:42:25,197
…para sa mas mahirap,

616
00:42:27,980 --> 00:42:29,097
o mas mayaman,

617
00:42:30,360 --> 00:42:31,822
sa sakit,

618
00:42:35,626 --> 00:42:36,800
at sa kalusugan.

619
00:42:39,617 --> 00:42:40,454
Ang magmahal...

620
00:42:40,900 --> 00:42:42,659
Dito rin.

621
00:42:47,271 --> 00:42:48,510
…at pahalagahan

622
00:42:50,160 --> 00:42:51,998
hanggang kamatayan ang maghihiwalay sa atin.

623
00:43:43,450 --> 00:43:47,856
Dalangin ko na maging matatag at mahaba ang inyong pagsasama
parang isang malakas na ilog.

624
00:43:49,297 --> 00:43:51,502
Ilagay mo ito sa iyong tahanan.

625
00:43:52,410 --> 00:43:53,939
Kailangan bang maging pato?

626
00:43:58,788 --> 00:43:59,997
Kayo po.

627
00:44:00,020 --> 00:44:01,798
Punta ka sa hagdan?

628
00:44:01,930 --> 00:44:03,297
Kumuha tayo ng ilang litrato.

629
00:44:18,377 --> 00:44:19,001
Pai.

630
00:44:19,690 --> 00:44:21,000
sana masaya ka.

631
00:44:21,835 --> 00:44:25,401
At sana alam mo
lahat ng meron ka sa buhay mo mahal ka.

632
00:44:26,334 --> 00:44:29,531
Lolo, Tita Kia, Papa at Mama,

633
00:44:30,560 --> 00:44:32,739
Tim, North…

634
00:44:32,780 --> 00:44:34,802
Paano naman ako? Bilangin mo ako.

635
00:44:36,700 --> 00:44:37,699
At si U, siyempre.

636
00:44:38,140 --> 00:44:39,502
Sana hindi mo sila i-take for granted.

637
00:44:41,653 --> 00:44:43,702
Tim.

638
00:44:44,297 --> 00:44:45,600
turn ko na ngayon?

639
00:44:45,674 --> 00:44:46,308
Oo.

640
00:44:47,715 --> 00:44:49,402
Tim.

641
00:44:50,571 --> 00:44:52,337
Dapat mahal mo si Pai.

642
00:44:53,330 --> 00:44:54,597
Ingatan mo siya.

643
00:44:55,139 --> 00:44:56,801
Ingatan mo ang kanyang pamilya.

644
00:44:56,937 --> 00:44:58,854
At huwag kalimutang mag-ingat
ng sarili mong pamilya.

645
00:44:59,097 --> 00:45:02,797
At higit sa lahat,
don't you dare hurt Pai again.

646
00:45:02,910 --> 00:45:03,697
Naririnig mo ako?

647
00:45:04,140 --> 00:45:05,038
Naririnig mo ako?

648
00:45:05,380 --> 00:45:06,496
Wag mo nang sasaktan ulit si Pai.

649
00:45:06,530 --> 00:45:09,001
-Halika dito, ikaw.
-Tim, ingat.

650
00:45:13,760 --> 00:45:14,710
Nasa camera kami.
ayos lang.

651
00:45:15,710 --> 00:45:17,502
Kunin mo siya nang madalas hangga't maaari.

652
00:45:18,750 --> 00:45:20,102
-Sapat na iyan.
-Ituloy mo, Tim.

653
00:45:20,299 --> 00:45:21,370
-Sabi ko sapat na.
-At sinabi ko na magpatuloy, Tim.

654
00:45:21,401 --> 00:45:22,697
Kasal tayo, alam mo ba?

655
00:45:22,810 --> 00:45:24,020
-Baby!
-Kaya ko pang gawin ito.

656
00:45:24,051 --> 00:45:24,742
ano?

657
00:45:25,385 --> 00:45:26,800
U, hindi natin sila mapapasama sa atin.

658
00:45:26,890 --> 00:45:28,500
-Baby!
-U, halika!

